html content paina padding untadi , and padding paina margin untadi , nee content ki padding kalipesi bayata border untadi


height:400 ante ah element height 400 avthadi
if height tho patu 
box-sizing: border-box; ---> idi pedithe element with its height and padding, border kalipi istadi (except margin enduku ante margin  is outside element kabatti
)

